				<header class="page-header">
					<h1 class="page-title">
													Monthly Archives: <span>June 2011</span>											</h1>
				</header>

				
								
					
	<article id="post-59" class="post-59 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-intelligence category-law category-machon category-media category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-spies category-talks-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-assange tag-cij tag-intelligence-2 tag-law-2 tag-machon tag-media-2 tag-mi5 tag-mi6 tag-spies-2 tag-tcij tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/06/keynote-at-centre-for-investigative-journalism-summer-school-16-july-2011-2.html" title="Permalink to Keynote at Centre for Investigative Journalism Summer School, 16 July 2011" rel="bookmark">Keynote at Centre for Investigative Journalism Summer School, 16 July 2011</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/06/keynote-at-centre-for-investigative-journalism-summer-school-16-july-2011-2.html" title="19:30" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-06-26T19:30:11+00:00" pubdate>June 26, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/06/keynote-at-centre-for-investigative-journalism-summer-school-16-july-2011-2.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e550903031883301538f73ed32970b-popup.html" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="display: inline;"><img alt="CIJ_logo_summerschool" border="0" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00e550903031883301538f73ed32970b image-full" src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e550903031883301538f73ed32970b-800wi.jpg" title="CIJ_logo_summerschool" /></a></p>
<p>My next talk in the <span class="caps">UK</span> will be a key­note at the renowned <a href="http://summerschools.tcij.org/pages/about_summerschool2011.htm" target="_self"><span class="caps">CIJ</span> sum­mer school</a> on 16<sup>th</sup> July. One of the major themes this year is whis­tleblow­ing, for obvi­ous Wikileaks-related reas­ons, and it appears I shall be in good company.</p>
<p>My talk is at 2pm on the Sat­urday.  I under­stand the key­notes are open to the pub­lic, not just sum­mer school attendees, so come along if you can and please spread the word!</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
