y/war-2" title="View all posts in War" rel="category tag">War</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/wikileaks" title="View all posts in Wikileaks" rel="category tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
