												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi5" title="View all posts in MI5" rel="category tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mossad" title="View all posts in Mossad" rel="category tag">Mossad</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/national-security" title="View all posts in National security" rel="category tag">National security</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/police" title="View all posts in Police" rel="category tag">Police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/shayler" title="View all posts in Shayler" rel="category tag">Shayler</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/acpo" rel="tag">ACPO</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cps" rel="tag">CPS</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/doherty" rel="tag">Doherty</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/dpp" rel="tag">DPP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/kennedy" rel="tag">kennedy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/npoiu" rel="tag">NPOIU</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/police-2" rel="tag">police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/starmer" rel="tag">Starmer</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/tomlinson" rel="tag">Tomlinson</a>			</span>
						
