				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/books" title="View all posts in Books" rel="category tag">Books</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi5" title="View all posts in MI5" rel="category tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mossad" title="View all posts in Mossad" rel="category tag">Mossad</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/national-security" title="View all posts in National security" rel="category tag">National security</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/police" title="View all posts in Police" rel="category tag">Police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/alami" rel="tag">Alami</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/botmeh" rel="tag">Botmeh</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/foot" rel="tag">Foot</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mossad" rel="tag">Mossad</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/peirce" rel="tag">Peirce</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/police-2" rel="tag">police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/shayler" rel="tag">Shayler</a>			</span>
						
